						"key": "jhaynie",
						"displayName": "Jeff Haynie",
						"active": false,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "{html}<div><p>(from <a href=\n\"/projects/32238/changesets/1a46446150e6b260016d427417d8be7b9f626b4f\"\ntitle=\n\"Changeset [1a46446150e6b260016d427417d8be7b9f626b4f]\">[1a46446150e6b260016d427417d8be7b9f626b4f]</a>)\n[<a href=\"/projects/32238/tickets/2737\" title=\n\"Ticket #2737\">#2737</a> state:fixed-in-qa] Attach to controller\nview, not window. Windows don't rotate. <a href=\n\"https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/1a46446150e6b260016d427417d8be7b9f626b4f\">\nhttps://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/1a46446150e6...</a></p></div>{html}",
